  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord community</h1><p>There you can share your pixel art, find a team, report bugs and keep up with all the news!<br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>PIXELS is the new way of pixel battles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>One world canvas</strong></li></ul>Players from all over the world paint on one scalable canvas.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Watch where the players are</strong></li></ul>Press TAB to see all the cursors. And other additional data.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>SUPER PIXELS</strong></li></ul>The brand-new animated pixels.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/c73fdca25b9ad32bdf69c1c9ab7145be.poster.avif?t=1735608493\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/c73fdca25b9ad32bdf69c1c9ab7145be.webm?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/c73fdca25b9ad32bdf69c1c9ab7145be.mp4?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Not just ONE pixel</strong></li></ul>You get a limit of 100 pixels and 10 super pixels. Cooldown depends on number of players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/9613f5457f37e804e87b8d8946f689e1.poster.avif?t=1735608493\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/9613f5457f37e804e87b8d8946f689e1.webm?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/9613f5457f37e804e87b8d8946f689e1.mp4?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Quick paint mode</strong></li></ul>Just press SHIFT and create.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/ae3e5771c41d129c4deea4d93207f21c.poster.avif?t=1735608493\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/ae3e5771c41d129c4deea4d93207f21c.webm?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/ae3e5771c41d129c4deea4d93207f21c.mp4?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Community features</strong></li></ul>Teams, users and ratings with leaderboard.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/16d59d75e8fe4d42676946674b526122.poster.avif?t=1735608493\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/16d59d75e8fe4d42676946674b526122.webm?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581610/extras/16d59d75e8fe4d42676946674b526122.mp4?t=1735608493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Share your art to the world.</i>",
